title: Chloe Khan displays results of 'secret nose job' while flaunting her cleavage and curves in clinging outfit
text:

Chloe Khan has reportedly undergone more surgery - but not for vanity reasons. 
The dark-haired star, 26, stepped out in Liverpool this week and revealed a new, slightly swollen nose. 
But sources said it wasn't for cosmetic reasons, instead it was to fix breathing problems. 
A source told the Sun Online : "Chloe recently underwent recent nose surgery to fix a deviated septum which was causing her severe sinus and breathing problems." (Photo: www.iCelebTV.com) (Photo: www.iCelebTV.com) (Photo: www.iCelebTV.com) 
"It wasnâ€™t for vanity reasons. Her nose is still very swollen and she is in the early stages of recovery." 
Busty Chloe was pictured making her way to a photoshoot in Liverpool to model Gaz Beadle and Aaron Chalmer's ASG line. 
She had all eyes firmly fixed her way as she got out of her white Range Rover in a plunging black top that exposed her cleavage and highlighted her slim waist. (Photo: www.iCelebTV.com) (Photo: www.iCelebTV.com) 
She teamed the tight top with black leggings, black socks and heels with clear straps. 
And despite being minutes away from getting her glam done for the shoot, Chloe's hair and make-up looked pretty on point. 
The confident babe then blew a kiss to camera as she made her way into a building. 
Of course, Chloe is no stranger to plastic surgery, having previously had a nose job and also a boob job when she took her bust to a huge 32HH. (Photo: www.iCelebTV.com) (Photo: www.iCelebTV.com) Couple Chloe Khan and Ashley Cain seen arriving at the Sixty6 Magazine launch party (Photo: FameFlynet) Chloe Khan enjoys a night out with friends at Gallery Nightclub Maidstone. Chloe is seen kissing a mystery man outside the club. (Photo: WENN.com) 
For the shoot, the Celebrity Big Brother star hung out in her lingerie as she spent time with Love Island 's Josh Ritchie and Ex On The Beach's ZaraLena Jackson. 
Chloe wore a pair of tiny black knickers, that exposed her bum and a black robe over a bra that accentuated her ample breasts, completing her all-black look with socks and trainers. 
ZaraLena wore a black leotard but gave herself a more covered-up look by tying a denim shirt around her waist. 
The concept for the shoot seemed to be inspired by Geordie Shore, which often sees them tucking into pizza after a heavy night on the drink.
